data.description: Back on the market with no fault to sellers.  MOTIVATED SELLERS!!   Sellers will pay closing cost for buyer up to $4000.00 with acceptable offer.  This home needs a little TLC but the price reflects.  Welcome to this Pfafftown home! Step inside and be greeted by hardwood floors that add a touch of elegance to the living spaces. The home has a spacious open living area with vaulted ceilings with natural light. This charming home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing comfort and convenience for everyone. The single-story layout provides easy living.  Sellers are offering a $650.00 allowance for buyer to purchase home warranty of their choice.
